========================================================================================================================
The Hippo Go Green distribution includes and bundles an installation of Apache Tomcat under folder tomcat.
Apache Tomcat is available under the Apache License, Version 2.0, but also comes with separate copyright notice and
license terms. Its usage is subject to the terms and conditions as described in the following files:

    tomcat-NOTICE
    tomcat-LICENSE

Note: if the above files contain references to specific sub-components within the tomcat application, then these
references are to be resolved relative to the tomcat/ folder.

========================================================================================================================
The Hippo Go Green distribution includes the 'cms' and 'site' web applications deployed under the folder tomcat/webapps/
of the bundled Tomcat installation. These web applications are available under the Apache License,
Version 2.0, but also come with separate copyright notices and license terms. Their usage is subject to
the terms and  conditions as described in the following files:

    cms-NOTICE
    cms-LICENSE
    site-NOTICE
    site-LICENSE

Note: if the above files contain references to sub-components within the web applications themselves, then these
references are to be resolved relative to the root location of the cms or site web application,
respectively tomcat/webapps/cms/ or tomcat/webapps/site/.

